I"Ê<h1 id="inertial-motion-sensorbmp280">Inertial Motion Sensor&amp;BMP280</h1>

<p>Please make a three digit time-meter with decimal, minimal function are described as follows:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Two buttons (implemented by interrupt) (Inputpins)
    <ul>
      <li>Clear (Reset)</li>
      <li>Start and stop</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Three digits of time display (Output pins)
    <ul>
      <li>Digit in tens</li>
      <li>Digit in ones</li>
      <li>Digit in first decimal places</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

